node.text: Anyone in Florida that’s wanted to train with my trainer @scottcamoin join us over at @f45_training_coralridge 👌When I am in town these functional high intensity classes will be the perfect supplement to my lifting. 💪 Grab your membership today and I’ll see ya there soon! 🙌 #fitness #f45 #fortlauderdale #florida #health #belowdeckmed

node.text: That’s a wrap! Hope everyone is enjoying this season of #belowdeckmed! There’s still a lot of excitement to come! I have to say this was the most fun I’ve had filming a season, thanks to the boat & production crew. A lot of work goes into making this show what it is and I’m grateful to be a part of it! ⚓️❤️ #belowdeck #greenscreen #thatsawrap #yachting #tv @bravotv
